nodes.text: Delequia was an Ithorian Female Jedi Master of the Jedi Order. During the Galactic War between the Galactic Republic and the reconstituted Sith Empire she was stationed on Ilum.
Delequia appears only in the game files for Star Wars: The Old Republic as  her character was cut from the game. Delequia's file can be found on Jedipedia.
